body:
Forgot to add that I founda folder .git 
C:\Projects\tensorflow\tensorflow\contrib\cmake\build\zlib\src\zlib\.git
That contains a config file:

[core]
	repositoryformatversion = 0
	filemode = false
	bare = false
	logallrefupdates = true
	symlinks = false
	ignorecase = true
[remote "origin"]
	url = https://github.com/madler/zlib
	fetch = +refs/heads/*:refs/remotes/origin/*
[branch "master"]
	remote = origin
	merge = refs/heads/master

Maybe it helps. Thanks.
